<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/19561990">关于精神病人访谈手记，心理疾病案例，有哪些值得推荐的好书？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4742" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


</div>
